parameters:
\nw[Taro]That huge body... that figure... the one from the
neighboring country, Misura, one of the Aegis,
Eater!
\nw[Kuno]Taro's parent's enemy... it's me!

\nw[Taro]No one is around... Could it be that all of our
allies have been wiped out!?
\nw[Kuno]It doesn't matter, I'll take revenge!
\nw[Kuno]Gasp!?
\nw[Taro]Too strong... Goboh...!

Kuno, who hasn't even joined the battle, is lying
there motionless.

I can't move anymore either. But there's no way
the Eaters will wait for me...
\nw[Taro](Is this as far as it goes...!)
\nw[Taro]...This...sound...
back_40_2

\nw[Nonna]It's incredibly hard, the blade can't cut through
it...
\nw[Taro]......Nonna!? Why are you here!?

\nw[Nonna]I finished my work early and was worried, so I
came to check. And then I saw this...

\nw[Nonna]I'll be the decoy. While I do that, take Kuno and
run away!
\nw[Taro]Then, Nonna...
\nw[Nonna]If I buy some time, I'll also withdraw. So hurry!
\nw[Taro]Understood...!
\nw[Nonna]\{Enhancement Magic: Forced Limit Break!\}

The difference in power and endurance is
incomparable, but it seems that Nonna is somehow
holding on with her skills and speed.

The Eaters are still faster, but it seems they
have no technique at all. They're just rampaging
with brute force like berserkers.
\nw[Taro]Now's the chance... guh!

The damage is too great, I can't even stand. But
still, I crawl towards Kuno.
\nw[Taro]Ah... Aahh...!

I was shocked when I saw Kuno. She is breathing
weakly, but it doesn't seem like it will last
long.

The amount of blood flowing is too much. Moreover,
the body is crushed. It's certain that the
internal organs have ruptured. It's almost
miraculous that she's still alive.

Unable to do anything, in the midst of such
despair, I held Kuno's hand. And then...
\nw[Kuno]...I'm sorry...sorry.
\nw[Taro]!
\nw[Kuno]We... made a promise...

I couldn't respond to those words. Kuno knows that
I am completely helpless. The truth is, there is
no way to help her.

\nw[Nonna]Ugh... Too strong...! Both of you, run away
quickly!
\nw[Taro]......
\nw[Taro]It's impossible...
\nw[Nonna]Don't give up!
\nw[Taro]No... with this wound... Kuno...
\nw[Nonna]......!

Nonna's anguish comes through. However, even so,
she quickly made a decisive judgment like a
seasoned mercenary.
\nw[Nonna]In that case, even if it's alone, run away!
\nw[Taro]There's no way...
\nw[The One Who Devours]\{\{\{Oooooohhhhhh!!!!\}
\nw[Nonna]......huh!
back_40_3
\nw[Nonna]Goa

The Eater's attack couldn't be completely avoided
and hit Nonna's leg. The Eater then launched
another attack at Nonna, causing her body to be
blown away like a ball and roll nearby.
\nw[Taro]Nonna!!

The Eater seemed to lose interest in us and ran
off to another location. There must be other prey
it wants to hunt.
However, such things didn't matter at all.

Nonna's lower body was crushed like paper. It
seems that her head also hit the ground when she
landed, as blood is flowing from her head.
Not even a twitch... she doesn't move at all.
\nw[Taro]Ah... aah... ah...
\nw[Taro]Aaaaaaaaahhhhhhhhhhhh!!!!!!
\nw[Taro]Kuno... Nonna...

Before I knew it, the sound of battle had
disappeared. I can't believe we defeated that
monster, but it's likely that we retreated
instead.

In the midst of that, a carefree voice that didn't
seem fitting for the situation could be heard.
tati_sirupu_001

\nw[???]Well well, when I tried to investigate the magical
power of the potential contractees, things took
quite a turn.
\nw[Taro]......

A stranger woman appeared, but I can't do
anything. I can't even think in the first place.

\nw[???]Hmm, there doesn't seem to be any energy or
response. However, the quality of the magic power
seems fine.

\nw[???]I don't know the situation, but are these people
important to you?

\nw[???]From what I can see, they're not on the verge of
death. Well, if it were me, I could probably heal
them.
\nw[Taro]......! I-Is that true!?

I tried to run over, but I tripped and fell. I
forgot that I was also seriously injured and
couldn't stand up.

If you look closely, it seems that the woman is
not a human. Could she be a demon?

If that's the case, then maybe I can heal them.
The magical power of the demon race is extremely
high, and they are also skilled in handling magic.

\nw[???]Hmm, it doesn't seem like we have time to have a
detailed conversation here. Let's stick to what's
necessary.

\nw[???]You should become my contractor. If those two are
important to you, I can help you with that.

\nw[Taro]Alright, I understand. How can I become a
contractor?

\nw[???]If you can answer immediately, that shows good
determination. As long as I can confirm your will,
there is nothing difficult.

\nw[???]Drink my blood. I will drink your blood. Then, I
will use the magic of the contract. It's different
from the original contract, but it's still
possible.
\nw[???]Look

The woman was bleeding so much that she cut her
own wrist and let the blood drip onto the ground.
She then brought it to my mouth.

I don't have time to hesitate. In order to save
the two of them, I immediately put my mouth on the
wound and sucked the woman's blood.
\nw[Taro]Ugh...

Suddenly, drowsiness struck. It became difficult
to maintain consciousness.
\nw[???]Go to sleep. I'll take care of the rest.

I felt my consciousness fading away as I listened
to those words.
